## SEO Requirements
- Every page needs meta tags
- Schema.org markup (LocalBusiness, Organization, FAQPage)
- Open Graph tags
- City-specific geo-targeting
- Mobile-first optimization

## Conversion Elements
- WhatsApp CTAs on every page (919884248927)
- Live waste counter showing losses
- Testimonials with specific savings amounts
- Urgency elements (limited spots)
- Trust badges (60-day guarantee)

## Development Principles
1. 100% AI-generated code
2. No external dependencies beyond core
3. Static generation preferred
4. Mobile-first responsive
5. Performance: <3s load time
6. Accessibility: WCAG AA compliant

## Key Personas
1. "Overwhelmed Owner" - Single outlet, 14-hour days
2. "Scaling Struggler" - 2-5 outlets, losing control
3. "Chain Champion" - 5+ outlets, seeking intelligence

## Content Guidelines
- Every number should be specific
- Use Indian context (₹, Indian cities, local food)
- Show transformation stories
- Before/After comparisons
- Emotional outcomes over features

